    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>[Congressional Record Volume 163, Number 194 (Wednesday, November 29, 2017)]From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. CULBERSON:H.R. 4477.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Article I, Section 8, Clause 4 and Article I, Section 8,Clause 18[Page H9516]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
